OL,3,CControversial low traffic
OL,4,Cneighbourhood scheme to be scrapped
OL,6,FSam Blackledge reports on the
OL,7,Fbeginning of the end for Exeter's low
OL,8,Ftraffic neighbourhood scheme
OL,10,FExeter's controversial low traffic
OL,11,Fneighbourhood scheme will be scrapped
OL,12,Fwithin weeks, after residents
OL,13,Fcampaigned and protested against it.
OL,15,FAt a packed meeting on Monday 3 June,
OL,16,Fcouncillors agreed that the trial -
OL,17,Fhas had a 'detrimental effect' and
OL,18,Fwill be abandoned.
