OL,3,CControversial low traffic
OL,4,Cneighbourhood scheme to be scrapped
OL,6,FAlmost 9,000 people responded to a
OL,7,Fconsultation, 82 per cent of whom were
OL,8,Fopposed to the scheme.
OL,10,FMany people said the LTNs had
OL,11,Fincreased congestion; made journeys
OL,12,Flonger or more difficult; and impacted
OL,13,Fcarers and disabled people.
OL,15,FBut others spoke during the meeting to
OL,16,Fsay it had been a boost for cyclists
OL,17,Fand walkers and would improve the
OL,18,Fenvironment.
