OL,3,CControversial low traffic
OL,4,Cneighbourhood scheme to be scrapped
OL,6,FIt was introduced with the aim of
OL,7,Fcutting pollution and encouraging
OL,8,Fsafety and public health.
OL,10,FCllr Carol Whitton, chair of the
OL,11,FExeter Highways and Traffic Orders
OL,12,FCommittee said: "I passionately
OL,13,Fbelieve that we have to change, we
OL,14,Fhave to move towards more sustainable
OL,15,Fforms of travel. Whether that is about
OL,16,Fclimate change or about Exeter as a
OL,17,Fcity.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
