OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1717529014
OL,3,CControversial low traffic
OL,4,Cneighbourhood scheme to be scrapped
OL,6,F"This was never a referendum, but the
OL,7,F(fact) that 80 per cent objected is a
OL,8,Ffigure that I, who believes in
OL,9,Fdemocracy, cannot ignore. People have
OL,10,Freached that decision, for whatever
OL,11,Freason, and there is only so much
OL,12,Fpushing uphill that politicians can
OL,13,Fdo."
OL,15,FCllr Rob Hannaford said: "In all the
OL,16,Fyears I have been on the council, I
OL,17,Fcannot remember a meeting that has
OL,18,Fbeen so charged, and I cannot remember
OL,19,Fan issue that has had such an effect
OL,20,Fon our city.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
