OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1717529014
OL,3,CControversial low traffic
OL,4,Cneighbourhood scheme to be scrapped
OL,6,F"The scheme has become toxic and we
OL,7,Fneed a new approach. The next
OL,8,Fgeneration does deserve safer streets."
OL,10,FCllr Adams added that some councillors
OL,11,Fhave been subjected to "hateful speech
OL,12,Fand threats" as a result of the trial.
OL,14,F"I have been told to rot in hell, I've
OL,15,Fseen people encouraging others to put
OL,16,Fexcrement through councillors' doors.
OL,17,FIf you want people to stand for you,
OL,18,Fwe need to debate robustly, but I
OL,19,Freally hope there's going to be a
OL,20,Fhealing process."
