OL,3,CControversial low traffic
OL,4,Cneighbourhood scheme to be scrapped
OL,6,FCouncillors agreed that the scheme
OL,7,Fwill end 'as soon as is practicable',
OL,8,Fand that road-narrowing planters will
OL,9,Fstay in place to slow down traffic.
OL,11,FPeople will still be encouraged to
OL,12,Fwalk or cycle where possible.
